text: José Llorens (born 2 February 1938) is a Spanish former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Spain Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Barcelona
